## 1. 🏫 School

**Route:** `/admin/content/schools`
**Backend:** `POST /api/admin/schools` · `PUT /api/admin/schools/{id}` · `DELETE /api/admin/schools/{id}`
**DB:** PostgreSQL [schools](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/admin.py#178-198) table
**Current:** 0 rows

| Field | Type | Required | Enum Values / Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| `name` | string(300) | ✅ | Full official name |
| `short_name` | string(100) | — | Abbreviation (e.g. "INSA") |
| `country_code` | string(5) | ✅ | FR, CA, DE, UK, ES, MA |
| `city` | string(100) | — | City name |
| `type` | enum | — | `university` · `grande_ecole` · `community_college` · `language_school` · `prep_school` |
| `is_public` | boolean | — | Default: true |
| `ranking_national` | integer | — | National ranking |
| `ranking_world` | integer | — | QS/THE world ranking |
| `tuition_international_yearly` | string(100) | — | e.g. "3,500 EUR/year" |
| `acceptance_rate` | decimal(5,2) | — | e.g. 15.50 |
| `has_moroccan_students` | boolean | — | Default: false |
| `application_platform` | string(100) | — | e.g. "Campus France", "Uni-Assist" |
| `scholarship_available` | boolean | — | Default: false |

