## 2. 📚 Program

**Route:** `/admin/content/programs`
**Backend:** `POST /api/admin/programs` · `PUT /api/admin/programs/{id}` · `DELETE /api/admin/programs/{id}`
**DB:** PostgreSQL [programs](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/admin.py#234-253) table
**Current:** 0 rows

| Field | Type | Required | Enum Values / Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| `school_id` | UUID | ✅ | FK → schools.id (pick from existing schools) |
| `name` | string(300) | ✅ | Program name |
| `degree_type` | enum | — | `licence` · `master` · `phd` · `dut` · `bts` · `cpge` · `diplome_ingenieur` · `mba` · `certificate` |
| `field_category` | string(100) | — | e.g. "Computer Science", "Business" |
| `language_of_instruction` | string(10) | — | [fr](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/auth.py#98-109) · [en](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/models/mentor.py#13-30) · [de](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminRoadmaps.jsx#75-85) · [ar](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/Onboarding.jsx#95-307) |
| `duration_months` | integer | — | e.g. 24, 36 |
| `admission_requirements` | JSON object | — | `{"gpa_min": 12, "bac_type": "S", "language_cert": "TCF B2"}` |
| `career_outcomes` | JSON array | — | `["Software Engineer", "Data Analyst"]` |
| `is_moroccan` | boolean | — | Default: false |

