## 4. 🗺️ Roadmap Template

**Route:** `/admin/content/roadmaps`
**Backend:** ❌ No CRUD endpoints (needs to be built)
**DB:** PostgreSQL `roadmap_templates` table
**Current:** 0 rows

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| `country_code` | string(5) | ✅ | FR, CA, DE, UK, TR |
| `pathway` | string(100) | ✅ | e.g. "campus_france", "direct_apply", "uni_assist" |
| `name` | string(300) | ✅ | e.g. "France — Campus France Pathway" |
| `total_steps` | integer | ✅ | Number of steps |
| `estimated_duration_weeks` | integer | — | e.g. 24 |
| `steps` | JSON array | ✅ | See step structure below |

**Step structure** (each item in `steps` array):
```json
{
  "order": 1,
  "title": "Créer un compte Campus France",
  "description": "Inscrivez-vous sur EtudesEnFrance...",
  "category": "application",
  "estimated_days": 3,
  "documents_needed": ["passeport", "relevés de notes"],
  "tips": "Commencez dès octobre"
}
```

