## 9. 🗣️ Language Course (MongoDB)

**Route:** No admin page yet
**Backend:** ❌ No CRUD endpoints
**DB:** MongoDB `language_courses` + `language_lessons` + `vocabulary`
**Current:** 2 courses, 3 lessons, 12 vocab

### language_courses

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| [language](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/learn.py#24-27) | string | ✅ | [fr](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/auth.py#98-109) · [en](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/models/mentor.py#13-30) · [de](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminRoadmaps.jsx#75-85) |
| `units` | array of objects | ✅ | See unit structure below |

**Unit structure:**
```json
{
  "unit": 1,
  "title": "Les Bases",
  "lessons": [
    {"lesson": 1, "title": "Greetings", "xp": 20},
    {"lesson": 2, "title": "Numbers", "xp": 25}
  ]
}
```

### language_lessons

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| [language](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/learn.py#24-27) | string | ✅ | [fr](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/auth.py#98-109) · [en](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/models/mentor.py#13-30) · [de](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminRoadmaps.jsx#75-85) |
| [unit](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/CommunityHub.jsx#11-161) | integer | ✅ | Unit number |
| [lesson](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/learn.py#53-61) | integer | ✅ | Lesson number |
| `exercises` | array of objects | ✅ | See exercise structure below |

**Exercise structure:**
```json
{
  "type": "translate",
  "prompt": "Translate: Hello",
  "answer": "Bonjour",
  "options": ["Bonjour", "Merci", "Au revoir"]
}
```

### vocabulary

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|-------|------|:---:|-----|
| [language](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/learn.py#24-27) | string | ✅ | [fr](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/routers/auth.py#98-109) · [en](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/backend/app/models/mentor.py#13-30) · [de](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminRoadmaps.jsx#75-85) |
