## What Needs to Be Built

### Backend (API endpoints)
1. Roadmap Templates CRUD (`/api/admin/roadmaps`)
2. Marketplace CRUD (`/api/admin/providers`)
3. Mentors CRUD (`/api/admin/mentors`)
4. Exam Questions CRUD (`/api/admin/questions`) — MongoDB
5. Career Paths CRUD (`/api/admin/careers`) — MongoDB
6. Language Content CRUD (`/api/admin/languages`) — MongoDB

### Frontend (Wire Save buttons)
1. Wire [AdminSchools.jsx](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminSchools.jsx) Save → `POST /api/admin/schools`
2. Wire [AdminPrograms.jsx](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminPrograms.jsx) Save → `POST /api/admin/programs`
3. Wire [AdminScholarships.jsx](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminScholarships.jsx) Save → `POST /api/admin/scholarships`
4. Wire [AdminRoadmaps.jsx](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/frontend/src/pages/AdminRoadmaps.jsx) Save → (needs backend first)
5. Complete form fields to match ALL schema fields
6. Add Edit/Delete action handlers
7. Build admin pages for Marketplace, Mentors, Career Paths, Questions, Languages
